      • andThen

        public void andThen(ExecutionCallback<V> callback)
        Description copied from interface: ICompletableFuture
        Registers a callback that will run after the future is completed. Please note that there is no ordering guarantee for running multiple callbacks. It is also not guaranteed that the callback will run within the same thread that completes the future.
        Specified by:
        andThen in interface ICompletableFuture<V>
        Parameters:
        callback - the callback to execute

        Specified by:
